from the People up into the Representatives.

Because without Representation
Right vs Left or Left vs Right

it is merely a figment of Our Imaginations!!!

We must Restore Representation,

And without a Constitutionally Elected and Formed Government, no other Rights Exist!

Because ALL of Our Enumerated Rights only Arise from the Power created by Our Constitution and from Our Constitutionally formed Representative Government.

and that is as UN-AMERICAN as it gets!

snippet.textDisplay: Dr. Sylvia Bignamini did not have the opportunity to explain the absence of immunity in this interview, mostly directed to the UK population that is already in lock down from what I understand .  I always want to explain things clearly to my patients if I expect compliance with a treatment, so it's not news to me to hear people wanting to understand.  In fact, it's normal and necessary for compliance I found.  Time magazine has a simple and nice explanation about this virus.  Simply said, the antibodies that are made in the human body, infected with  Covid 19 infection DO NOT BIND STRONGLY to the protein spikes of the virus.  It's like using a "water gun against the Exterminator".  The lack of binding of the antibody to the virus prevents people from getting immunity.  Most viruses induce an antibody that binds to them, and that's how we create vaccines.    This is not the case with Covid19, and as we fight to save lives and to find out treatment, what we know for sure is that isolation in the home not only helps prevention, but also shortens the time of recovery of the infected person.
